tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE community_center(
   member_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   member_name VARCHAR(50),
   membership_type VARCHAR(20),
   join_date DATE,
   facility_usage_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE FacilityUsage (
    usage_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    member_id INT REFERENCES Members(member_id),
    facility_name VARCHAR(50),
    usage_date DATE,
    usage_time TIME
);

CREATE TABLE Members (
    member_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name TEXT,
    last_name TEXT,
    birthday DATE,
    email TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Facilities (
    facility_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    facility_name TEXT,
    address TEXT,
    capacity INT,
    usage_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE Facility_Usage (
    usage_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    facility_id INT,
    member_id INT,
    usage_date DATE,
    hours_used INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (facility_id) REFERENCES Facilities(facility_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (member_id) REFERENCES Members(member_id)
);

CREATE TABLE member_facility_usage ( 
    usage_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    member_id INT, 
    facility_id INT, 
    usage_date DATE, 
    duration_minutes INT 
);

CREATE TABLE facility_statistics ( 
    stat_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    facility_id INT, 
    average_daily_usage INT, 
    peak_usage_date DATE, 
    total_usage_count INT 
);
CREATE TABLE Members (member_id INT PRIMARY KEY, first_name VARCHAR(50), last_name VARCHAR(50), email VARCHAR(100), phone_number VARCHAR(15), join_date DATE);
CREATE TABLE Membership_Types (membership_type_id INT PRIMARY KEY, type_name VARCHAR(50), monthly_fee DECIMAL(10,2);
CREATE TABLE Facilities (facility_id INT PRIMARY KEY, facility_name VARCHAR(100), location VARCHAR(100), capacity INT);
CREATE TABLE Facility_Usage (usage_id INT PRIMARY KEY, facility_id INT, member_id INT, usage_date DATE, start_time TIME, end_time TIME);
CREATE TABLE Statistics (stat_id INT PRIMARY KEY, facility_id INT, total_usage INT, average_usage DECIMAL(10,2), month_year DATE);
